---
title: Jammy Pork Chops with Shallot-Thyme Pan Stuffing & Roasted Green Beans
description: Another work day, another dinner daydream. You know what we mean. You’re sitting at your desk and 2:00 p.m. rolls around. Suddenly, all you can think is, “Dinner...what the heck am I going to eat for dinner?!” Well, we’ve got you covered, and FYI, the answer to that question is pretty darn delicious. We’re serving up tender pork chops with custardy shallot-thyme pan stuffing (psst—that’s stuffing made in a pan!) and crisp roasted green beans. To finish things off, the pork is drizzled with a life-affirming fig jam sauce. Talk about a dream come true!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/jammy-pork-chops-59e5bcf1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/jammy-pork-chops-5ee7dae62e97aa233065b639-867ef82e.pdf
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 730 kcal
